### Capitalist API2 - IntelliJ IDEA HTTP Client
### Select the `dev` environment before running requests.

### Read whitelist
< {% import { signCapitalistRequest } from "./sign-capitalist.js"; signCapitalistRequest(request, crypto); %}
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/whitelist
API-Key: {{apiKey}}
X-Request-Timestamp: {{timestamp}}
Signature: {{signature}}



